    answer: "Yes! We provide commercial cleaning services for businesses in Clements and throughout Limestone County. From small offices to larger facilities, we can clean after hours or on weekends. We offer daily, weekly, or monthly commercial cleaning schedules."
  },
  {
    question: "How much does house cleaning in Clements cost?",
