    question: "Do you offer recurring cleaning schedules?",
    answer: "Yes! Most of our Clements clients choose weekly or bi-weekly cleaning. Recurring clients get preferred pricing and scheduling priority. You'll have the same team each visit on the same day, so you always know when to expect us."
  },
